(23, 1, '2017-11-13 06:20:14', '2017-11-13 06:20:14', '[vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text el_class="inner-page-left"]\r\n<h2>Services</h2>\r\n<a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/our-physicians/">Our Providers</a> have extensive experience caring for patients from young adulthood through geriatrics. Cholla Medical Group-Primary Care provides:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Adult primary care</li>\r\n 	<li>Wellness and preventive care</li>\r\n 	<li>Management of chronic conditions</li>\r\n 	<li>Same-day appointments</li>\r\n 	<li>Well woman exams/Pap smear/Routine breast exams</li>\r\n 	<li>Preoperative Evaluation</li>\r\n 	<li>Coumadin/Anticoagulation clinic (fingerstick INR checks)</li>\r\n 	<li>Vaccines (Flu, Pneumonia, Tetanus, Shingles)</li>\r\n 	<li>EKG</li>\r\n 	<li>Onsite lab for blood work</li>\r\n 	<li>Blood glucose level testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Urine testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Pulse oximeter (oxygen level testing)</li>\r\n 	<li>Breathing treatments</li>\r\n 	<li>Blood pressure checks</li>\r\n 	<li>Wound care</li>\r\n 	<li>Skin biopsies</li>\r\n 	<li>Cryotherapy for wart removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Suture removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Earwax removal</li>\r\n 	<li>Vision exams</li>\r\n 	<li>Exams for professional driver’s certification</li>\r\n 	<li>Handicap placards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur physicians have a special interest in many subspecialties of medicine including cardiovascular disease, diabetes,hypertension,thyroid disease, and more.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" el_class="inner-page-right"][vc_column_text el_class="inner-page-right"]\r\n<ul class="section-pages">\r\n 	<li><a href="#">Services</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="#">Health and Wellness Recommendations</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="#">Adult Immunization Guidelines</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'services', '', '', '2017-11-16 09:16:04', '2017-11-16 09:16:04', '', 0, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/?p