(112, 1, '2017-11-14 12:48:25', '2017-11-14 12:48:25', '<div class="container-fluid">\r\n<div class="container section-main">\r\n<div class="row">\r\n<div class="section-wrk-main">\r\n<div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 quick-links">\r\n<h2>Quick Links</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="#">For New Patients</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/accepted-insurances/">Accepted Insurances</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/rate-your-visit/">Rate Your Visit</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="#">Practice News</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 our-mission">\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\nWe provide quality primary care in a warm and family-friendly atmosphere. We respect our patients by running on time and we stand with them through all the medical moments of their lives.\r\n<h2>Practice News</h2>\r\nCholla Medical Group-Primary Care will be hosting our annual flu shot clinic this year. The clinic is exclusively for our patients on a walk-in basis.\r\n<h6>PLEASE BRING YOUR MOST CURRENT INSURANCE CARD.</h6>\r\n<p class="txt-center">If you cannot make it to our walk-in clinic, please call the office at 480-418-7246 to schedule an appointment or you can visit any pharmacy for your annual flu shot. We ask that you contact our office at 480-418-7246 update your provider that you have received your flu shot.</p>\r\n<a href="#">Read More...</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-sm-4 col-xs-12 partner-health">\r\n<h2>Your Partner In Health</h2>\r\nWe encourage our patients to take an active role in their health. Annual wellness exams, preventative screening tests, medication reviews, effective communication regarding developments in care, healthy lifestyle habits, and active participation in their own health education are important ways our patients can improve the quality of their healthcare and the quality of their lives.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-14 12:48:25', '2017-11-14 12:48:25', '', 5, 'http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/5-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2017-11-14 12:55:39', '2017-11-14 12:55:39', '[vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text el_class="inner-page-left"]\r\n<h2>For New Patients</h2>\r\n<h6>Welcome to Cholla Medical Group-Primary Care!</h6>\r\nOur goal is to provide you with the best patient care and service. We invite you to begin your new patient registration now by following these directions:\r\n<h6>1. Make an appointment</h6>\r\nFor your convenience, you may<a href="#"> schedule an appointment online</a>. Appointments may also be made by calling (480) 418-7246.\r\n<h6>2.Fill out the new patient forms</h6>\r\nPlease <a href="#">download and complete the new patient packet</a> and bring it with you to your first appointment.\r\n<h6>3. Send us your medical records</h6>\r\nIf you have your records, please fax them to (480) 304-3534, or bring them to our office at least one week prior to your appointment so your physician can review them and prepare for your visit.\r\n<h6>4 Prepare for your office visit</h6>\r\nIn addition to completing the forms, we will also require the following for your first visit:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Driver’s License or other valid government-issued photo identification</li>\r\n 	<li>Insurance card</li>\r\n 	<li>Any co-pay, deductibles or co-insurance applicable to your health plan</li>\r\n 	<li>Prescription medication bottles, as well as any vitamins and supplements</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h6>5. Get directions to our office</h6>\r\nFind a <a href="#">map of the location</a> where you will see your physician and get personalized driving directions.\r\n<h6>6. We look forward to seeing you!</h6>\r\nPlease arrive at least 30 minutes early if you have not yet filled out these forms. If you have completed forms with you, you only need to check in with the reception desk 15 minutes before your scheduled appointment.\r\n\r\nThank you for your assistance completing this information. We look forward to seeing you![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text el_c