(187, 1, '2017-11-15 12:12:02', '2017-11-15 12:12:02', '[vc_row][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text el_class="inner-page-left"]\r\n<h2>About Our Practice</h2>\r\nAt Cholla Medical Group-Primary Care, we provide quality primary care in a warm and family-friendly atmosphere. We respect our patients by running on time and we stand with them through all the medical moments of their lives.\r\n\r\nOur providers are caring experts in evidence based preventative care for adults. When medical problems do occur, we have the expertise in the management of acute and chronic medical conditions. We have extensive experience in the treatment of diabetes, heart disease, high blood pressure, thyroid problems, hormone imbalances, cholesterol control, weight management, skin problems, pre-operative evaluations, pain management, asthma, emphysema, infections, arthritis, and most medical conditions.\r\n\r\nWe offer convenient access to a wide range of <a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/services/">services</a>.\r\n\r\nWhen specialist care is required, we will refer you to the top specialists in the Valley and help coordinate your care.\r\n\r\nWe encourage our patients to take an active role in their health. Annual wellness exams, preventative screening tests, medication reviews, effective communication regarding developments in care, healthy ifestyle habits, and active participation in their own health education are important ways our patients can improve the quality of their healthcare and the quality of their lives.\r\n\r\nWe are Partners in Your Care.\r\n\r\nTogether, we can help you achieve the healthiest possible version of yourself. You, and your loved ones, deserve it.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text el_class="inner-page-right"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/about-us/">About Our Practice</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href="http://webdesigndemo1.com/cholla-medical/about-us/">What is Internal Medicine?<